the hell out of myself.

56:44.025 --> 56:45.527
[man] What are the judges looking for?

56:45.610 --> 56:48.196
[Arnold] Well, they're looking
for proportions, symmetry,

56:48.279 --> 56:49.406
the size of the muscles,

56:49.489 --> 56:51.241
how you can pose and present the muscles.

56:51.324 --> 56:54.244
I want to put some effort out
to help people understand

56:54.327 --> 56:55.745
what the sport is all about.

56:55.829 --> 56:58.915
-[man] Got everything in the chair now?
-No, there was a problem.

56:58.998 --> 57:00.208
-I see.
-[audience laughs]

