57:56.890 --> 57:58.433
[cheering and applause]

57:59.309 --> 58:03.354
[Arnold] In 1974,
I won the Mr. Olympia competition.

58:03.438 --> 58:07.233
So I won, all together,
13 world bodybuilding championships,

58:08.276 --> 58:09.569
