58:24.334 --> 58:25.543
To win another one?

58:26.544 --> 58:27.629
Boring.

58:28.796 --> 58:30.131
So I stopped.

58:31.174 --> 58:33.176
[applause]

58:34.219 --> 58:37.430
I mean, I'm competing now for 10 years.

58:37.514 --> 58:40.642
And after 10 years,
I feel like it's enough, you know?

58:41.392 --> 58:43.645
You have to let
other people have a chance

58:44.521 --> 58:47.732
and, uh, just leave as a winner.

58:50.235 --> 58:53.446
